# ðŸ§  PART 1: STRING HANDLING QUESTIONS (READ ONLY)

## Topic 1: Basic Strings

1. Define a string and print it.
2. Concatenate two strings and print.

## Topic 2: String Interpolation

3. Use a variable inside a sentence using interpolation.
4. Show difference between single quotes and double quotes.

## Topic 3: Split Strings

5. Split a string using `/` and print second part.
6. Print last part of a split string (dynamic index).

## Topic 4: Replace Strings

7. Replace a character in a string.
8. Replace multiple characters using `replaceAll`.

## Topic 5: Substring & Length

9. Extract first 4 characters from a string.
10. Print length of a string.

## Topic 6: Case Conversion

11. Convert string to uppercase.
12. Convert string to lowercase.

## Topic 7: Trim & Cleanup

13. Remove extra spaces from a string.

## Topic 8: Real CI/CD Usage

14. Create Docker image tag using string interpolation.
15. Create deploy message using env + string ops.

